# Invitation for Intervention


## Get all emails associated to interventions


### Resource

`<%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/v1/interventions/:intervention_id/invitations`


### URL parameters

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------
intervention_id | Intervention ID | yes


### Query String

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### HTTP request method

`GET`


### HTTP headers

<%= partial 'includes/http/headers/auth' %>


### HTTP body


### Note


> HTTP example request

```http
GET <%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/v1/interventions/1/invitations
```

```http
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
access-token: xxxyyyzzz
token-type: Bearer
client: xxxyyyzzz
uid: user@<%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>
```


> HTTP response 200 OK


